+# Production Readiness Checklist
+
+Complete this checklist before deploying to production.
+
+## Backend Configuration
+
+- [ ] **Database URL**: Backend is configured with proper PostgreSQL database
+  - [ ] Database is backed up
+  - [ ] Credentials are strong and stored securely (via environment variables)
+  - [ ] Connection pooling is configured
+
+- [ ] **Environment Variables**: All required backend env vars are set
+  ```bash
+  DB_URL=postgresql://...
+  DB_USERNAME=...
+  DB_PASSWORD=...
+  JWT_SECRET=... (strong, random string)
+  FRONTEND_BASE_URL=https://yourdomain.com
+  CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://yourdomain.com
+  ```
+
+- [ ] **CORS Configuration**: 
+  - [ ] `CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS` set to your frontend domain (not localhost)
+  - [ ] Verified with a test request from frontend
+
+- [ ] **Security Settings**:
+  - [ ] Running with profile: `spring.profiles.active=prod`
+  - [ ] API docs disabled: `API_DOCS_ENABLED=false`
+  - [ ] JWT secret is NOT the default development secret
+  - [ ] Error details hidden: `server.error.include-message=never`
+  - [ ] Production checks enabled: `PRODUCTION_CHECKS_ENABLED=true`
+
+- [ ] **SSL/TLS**: 
+  - [ ] Backend accessible via HTTPS
+  - [ ] Valid SSL certificate installed
+
+- [ ] **Logging**:
+  - [ ] Security logging level set appropriately (WARN or less)
+  - [ ] Log aggregation configured (optional but recommended)
+
+- [ ] **Rate Limiting**:
+  - [ ] Enabled: `RATE_LIMIT_ENABLED=true`
+  - [ ] Appropriate limits set for authentication endpoints
+
+- [ ] **Email Configuration**:
+  - [ ] Email service configured (Gmail, SendGrid, custom SMTP)
+  - [ ] Credentials set via environment variables
+  - [ ] Sender email address verified with provider
+
+## Frontend Configuration
+
+- [ ] **Environment Variables**:
+  - [ ] `.env.production` created with production API URL
+  ```bash
+  VITE_API_URL=https://api.yourdomain.com/api
+  ```
+
+- [ ] **Build Verification**:
+  ```bash
+  npm run build  # Should complete without errors
+  npm run preview  # Should work without localhost references
+  ```
+
+- [ ] **No Hardcoded Values**:
+  - [ ] No hardcoded `localhost` addresses
+  - [ ] No development-only URLs in code
+  - [ ] All environment-specific config uses env variables
+
+- [ ] **Console & Debugging**:
+  - [ ] No `console.log()` statements in production bundles
+  - [ ] DebugInfo component won't display in production
+  - [ ] Source maps disabled
+
+- [ ] **Performance**:
+  - [ ] Bundle size is reasonable (check with `npm run preview`)
+  - [ ] Page loads quickly
+  - [ ] No memory leaks in components
+  - [ ] Images are optimized
+
+- [ ] **Security**:
+  - [ ] `.env` files in `.gitignore`
+  - [ ] No sensitive data in version control
+  - [ ] No hardcoded API keys or tokens
+  - [ ] HTTPS enforced in production URL
+
+## Deployment
+
+- [ ] **Platform Setup**:
+  - [ ] Hosting account created (Vercel, Netlify, AWS, etc.)
+  - [ ] Domain name registered and configured
+  - [ ] SSL certificate provisioned
+
+- [ ] **Frontend Deployment**:
+  - [ ] Build command configured: `npm run build`
+  - [ ] Output/publish directory: `dist`
+  - [ ] Environment variable `VITE_API_URL` configured on platform
+  - [ ] Deployment triggers set up for automatic deploys (optional)
+
+- [ ] **SPA Routing Configuration**:
+  - [ ] Web server configured to serve `index.html` for all routes
+  - [ ] Tested navigation to nested routes (e.g., `/admin/properties`)
+
+- [ ] **DNS & Domain**:
+  - [ ] Domain DNS points to hosting provider
+  - [ ] SSL certificate valid and auto-renewing
+  - [ ] Tested from multiple locations globally
+
+## Testing
+
+- [ ] **User Registration & Login**:
+  - [ ] Can register new account
+  - [ ] Can login with credentials
+  - [ ] Can logout
+  - [ ] Can reset password
+
+- [ ] **Property Features**:
+  - [ ] Can view property list
+  - [ ] Can view property details with map
+  - [ ] Can book appointments
+  - [ ] Search and filters work
+
+- [ ] **Admin Features**:
+  - [ ] Can access admin panel (must be admin user)
+  - [ ] Can create property
+  - [ ] Can edit property
+  - [ ] Can delete property
+  - [ ] Can view appointments
+  - [ ] Can manage users
+
+- [ ] **Cross-Browser Testing**:
+  - [ ] Chrome/Edge
+  - [ ] Firefox
+  - [ ] Safari
+  - [ ] Mobile browsers (iOS Safari, Chrome Mobile)
+
+- [ ] **API Communication**:
+  - [ ] All API calls work (check Network tab in DevTools)
+  - [ ] No CORS errors
+  - [ ] Authentication tokens work correctly
+  - [ ] Redirects to login on 401
+
+- [ ] **Error Scenarios**:
+  - [ ] No 404 errors for valid routes
+  - [ ] Error messages are user-friendly
+  - [ ] Missing images/assets handled gracefully
+
+## Monitoring & Maintenance
+
+- [ ] **Monitoring Setup**:
+  - [ ] Error tracking configured (Sentry, Rollbar, etc.) - Optional
+  - [ ] Analytics configured (Google Analytics, Plausible, etc.) - Optional
+  - [ ] Uptime monitoring enabled
+
+- [ ] **Backup & Recovery**:
+  - [ ] Database backups configured (daily)
+  - [ ] Backup tested by restoring
+  - [ ] Recovery procedure documented
+
+- [ ] **Updates & Security**:
+  - [ ] Dependency updates scheduled (monthly)
+  - [ ] Security patches applied promptly
+  - [ ] SSL certificate renewal automated
+
+- [ ] **Documentation**:
+  - [ ] Deployment procedure documented in DEPLOYMENT.md
+  - [ ] API documentation available
+  - [ ] Runbook created for common issues
+
+## Performance Optimization
+
+- [ ] **Frontend Performance**:
+  - [ ] Lighthouse score: A (90+)
+  - [ ] Core Web Vitals: Good
+  - [ ] First Contentful Paint < 2s
+  - [ ] Largest Contentful Paint < 2.5s
+
+- [ ] **Backend Performance**:
+  - [ ] API response time < 200ms for most endpoints
+  - [ ] Database queries optimized (indexes created)
+  - [ ] Connection pooling configured
+
+- [ ] **Caching Strategy**:
+  - [ ] Browser caching enabled for static assets
+  - [ ] CDN configured (optional but recommended)
+  - [ ] API response caching where appropriate
+
+## Security Audit
+
+- [ ] **Authentication & Authorization**:
+  - [ ] JWT tokens properly validated
+  - [ ] Admin routes protected
+  - [ ] No hardcoded credentials anywhere
+  - [ ] Password hashing strong (bcrypt/Argon2)
+
+- [ ] **Data Protection**:
+  - [ ] HTTPS enforced (all traffic encrypted)
+  - [ ] Sensitive data not logged
+  - [ ] PII handled securely
+  - [ ] Database encrypted at rest (if required)
+
+- [ ] **Input Validation**:
+  - [ ] Frontend validates input
+  - [ ] Backend validates/sanitizes input
+  - [ ] Protection against SQL injection
+  - [ ] Protection against XSS
+
+- [ ] **API Security**:
+  - [ ] CORS properly configured
+  - [ ] Rate limiting enabled
+  - [ ] Request size limits set
+  - [ ] API authentication required
+
+## Post-Launch
+
+- [ ] Monitor error rates and uptime
+- [ ] Collect user feedback
+- [ ] Monitor performance metrics
+- [ ] Plan for scale (load testing, horizontal scaling)
+- [ ] Regular security audits
+- [ ] Keep dependency versions updated
+
+---
+
+## Sign-Off
+
+- [ ] Development team sign-off
+- [ ] QA team sign-off  
+- [ ] Product/Business owner approval
+- [ ] Security review completed
+
+**Launched on**: _______________  
+**By**: _______________  
+**Version**: 0.0.1
